{"tid":1049133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"男子地鐵上撫摸女伴     女子閉眼嬌喘畫面激情","createTime":"2019-03-06T05:18:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-09T05:14:43.000Z","uid":39464,"like":787,"dislike":237,"uniUserReply":106,"replies":[{"pid":"900a835cd65d6aafff89556e3d8efba9c3b9536a","tid":1049133,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:18:41.000Z","msg":"情侶間有時候愛如潮水的時候真的會做出令人「凍未條」的舉動，近日臉書專頁「Our Singapore」分享了一段情侶在大眾運輸系統內上下其手愛的過火的影片，令人看的臉紅心跳。<br />\n<br />\n影片中，一對男女在地鐵上情不自禁，男子將左手摸上了女子胸前的豐滿，並利用食指與拇指雙重加壓下，挑逗著女子的私密點，這也讓女子忘情的閉上雙眼露出極度享受的神情，更不時夾雜著急促的嬌喘聲，彷彿如魚得水。<br />\n<br />\n而影片曝光後，讓不少網友紛紛留言回覆「那女的很爽」、「這才是真愛」、「屠龍勇士」、「女生看起來應該很享受」、「馴龍高手」、「2019年最佳色情片」、「不能只有我看到」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/03/05/1810677-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F03%2F05%2F1810677-XXL.jpg&h=10a38c4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=507670\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D507670&d=iefYBA3dMTKG%2BriJzBrQhZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=0f23df7e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2Fm%2Fnews.aspx%3Fnewsid%3D507670&h=707cda55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/m/news.aspx?newsid=507670</a>"},{"pid":"1da884f2f0f2a6ee5eacbd4a5b98bee6fe8f800e","tid":1049133,"uid":179467,"like":589,"dislike":7,"score":582,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:19:23.000Z","msg":"兩條肉蟲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"305256bc6618326b881ff0905b535f403a6f6bc1","tid":1049133,"uid":76115,"like":26,"dislike":393,"score":-367,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:20:29.000Z","msg":"張圖睇得出條女個嘴係靚女個種嘴型來<br />\n減下肥應該有救"},{"pid":"ab4fb68d17c2fe4e3911d6cb936b8efeb551b372","tid":1049133,"uid":21423,"like":33,"dislike":166,"score":-133,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已